{"tid":1634060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得搞交通會令人罷工嗰啲係咪香港人黎？","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T11:11:24.000Z","uid":24998,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4a748eaec5544929fb757c7d617c5578ab1eb2c7","tid":1634060,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:23:35.000Z","msg":"咁多年黎<br />\n除非啲打工仔老細話唔洗返 <br />\n如果唔係既話班打工仔爬山都爬返工啦<br />\n<br />\n所以搞交通想令佢地被罷工根本唔可行<br />\n佢地只會覺得係被阻返工<br />\n對示威者既印象會差左 <br />\n對個大局根本弊多於利<br />\n<br />\n真係想再三罷<br />\n最起碼要係文宣途徑去做<br />\n唔係話依家無<br />\n但比起早兩個月文宣真係少左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff548d9aff560c59b4a6e35f59f74f7141cddc3","tid":1634060,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"自推1/5"},{"pid":"a5b844698caf578b4c92f4b869b67ebe9466753e","tid":1634060,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:27:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6876bb65c0b1704ea00ff16bbd56c6103401ba7f","tid":1634060,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:28:23.000Z","msg":"自推2/5"},{"pid":"b1b4243969c405ccea929e4ea613bd6baa4fce74","tid":1634060,"uid":71034,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:29:27.000Z","msg":"你有眼睇依幾日有幾多舖頭係有開門架?"},{"pid":"28f79d7873333410826c41b072e41f8957a8d2f4","tid":1634060,"uid":321913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:30:31.000Z","msg":"我係香港人<br />\n支持拆鐵 <br />\n助攻三罷"},{"pid":"c0d2d7d8e361d226d6b9518622fc8810a9818a10","tid":1634060,"uid":299573,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:35:32.000Z","msg":"我都覺，我地可以說服人罷工，但係癱瘓黨鐵強制人罷工只會令人反感，愈黎愈少人支持運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39e0cbdfa541f7bed12fd4a199053e075cc252f","tid":1634060,"uid":127872,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"自願罷工同被動罷工根本好大分別。<br />\n坦白講句，被動罷工罷得幾多日？三幾日影響有限，但就會令市民覺得示威者影響民生。"},{"pid":"8a938e9b5a20803d9c301fa1848ae77b09ce74d3","tid":1634060,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1b4243969c405ccea929e4ea613bd6baa4fce74","tid":1634060,"uid":71034,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:29:27.000Z","msg":"你有眼睇依幾日有幾多舖頭係有開門架?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"同時呢兩日都引起左好大爭議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多人只係被罷工"},{"pid":"7a9966b1d0037b681d24fe4a218678d437a58885","tid":1634060,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"自推3/5"},{"pid":"97aff74fee5616602eedc4282b12fec951ba75b1","tid":1634060,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:56:05.000Z","msg":"自推4/5"},{"pid":"b7bfe3facdbf737c3445bc8ebc68ba49eb7251b4","tid":1634060,"uid":24998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:00:34.000Z","msg":"自推5/5 完"},{"pid":"d4186bf68a769bc53faabaa5f1e621d7b42fc882","tid":1634060,"uid":66870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"係popo打"}]}